w schedule SMS/text messages in addition to email.</p>
<p>What changed</p>
<p>Email Plans can now schedule one SMS or a series of SMS messages.</p>
<p>SMS can be sent to Leads and Contacts.</p>
<p>Why it matters</p>
<p>Teams using Email Plans for timed outreach can now manage email + SMS follow-ups through the same scheduling workflow, reducing manual reminders and keeping contact sequences consistent.</p>
<p>Learn more: <a href="https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/392">https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/392</a></p>
